description:
Come on out to the iconic Q20 where drinks are cheap and you can bring in any food - including from the convenient aisles of QFC! Enjoy one of the three routes and the company of good people!

9mi | 800' | Pace Groups 7:45, 8:30 10+/-

Post-Social at Q20 (QFC bar)

Headlamp! 

Note: you may want to bring  your own navigation in case there are not enough leaders due to the holidays
title: Thirsty Seconds | Q20
